<item>
            <title>[LU-13164] remove unused LUSTRE_DIRECTIO_FL</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13164</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;LUSTRE_DIRECTIO_FL&lt;/tt&gt; was added from the upstream kernel &lt;tt&gt;FS_DIRECTIO_FL&lt;/tt&gt; in the hopes that it might be useful, but it has since been removed from the upstream kernel in commit v4.4-rc4-22-g68ce7bfcd995 and replaced by &lt;tt&gt;FS_VERITY_FL&lt;/tt&gt; using the same value in commit v5.3-rc2-4-gfe9918d3b228.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since we have never used this flag in Lustre, there is no risk to remove it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
